data.description: The Maple Plan features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms with generous 2nd Floor Loft Space! Upgraded Laminate Hardwoods adorn the entire 1st Floor along with Oak Treads on Stairwell. Gas Fireplace in Great Rm, Laundry Rm on 1st floor right off of the garage entry area. Deluxe Kitchen with Admiral Navy Cabinetry & Quartz Countertops, Stainless Double Wall Ovens & Gas Cooktop with Hood! Primary BathRm with Tiled Walls & Semi-Frameless Shower, Kitchen Backsplash, Exterior Flood Light and Gorgeous Siding Color of Slate with Summer Breeze Front Door & Tuxedo Gray Shutters. Single Undermount Stainless Kitchen Sink with Upgraded Faucet, Brushed Nickel Lighting, Covered patio. HERS SCORE 55. Energy Star Certified Home
